stripTags

public List<JavaComment> stripTags(Set<String> tagNames,
                                   List<JavaComment> originals)
Produce a copy of a list of comments where all javadoc comments have had the specified tags removed. Non javadoc comments are left alone.

Parameters:
tagNames - Set of tag names (including leading @) to be removed
originals - List of Comments to be processed
Returns:
a new list of comments with the specified tags removed

paramDoc

public List<JavaComment> paramDoc(String paramName,
                                  List<JavaComment> originals)
Produce a copy of a list of JavaDoc comments by pulling specified parameter tags out of an orignal list of comments. Block and EOL comments are skipped. JavaDoc comments are stripped down to only have the content of the specified param tag

leftAlign

public List<JavaComment> leftAlign(List<JavaComment> originals)
Align a list of comments on the left marging. EOLComments are left alone. Block and JavaDoc comments are aligned by making every line that starts with a * be one space in from the comment opener. Lines that don't start with * are left alone.
